item.title: Anyone got the compiler for ajscape?
item.dc:creator: @allamericanboy82 allamericanboy82
item.description:
@allamericanboy82 wrote:

download java 6 update 10 and dont use the download manager just click the offline link and download it that way then put this compiler in yours it will work for sure @echo off
title Client Compiler
if exist “%programfiles%\Java” (call :compile “%programfiles%\Java”) else (goto error)
:compile
for /D %%x in ("%~1jdk*") do (set p="%%~x\bin\javac.exe")
if defined p (%p% -cp . *.java)
if defined p (goto end)
:error
echo You do not have Java installed. Please download it at the site that is about to load.
“%programfiles%\Internet Explorer\iexplore.exe” http://java.sun.com/javase/downloads/index.jsp
:end
echo Finished!
pause
exit////////////////////////////////////////////////////Rune Gods///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
